title: "C'mon, Shinzo... they've paid me a fortune!"
description: Trump holds national security talks in a crowded Mar-a-Lago ballroom. Flynn and Priebus are on the ropes. And DeRay McKesson joins Jon, Jon, and Tommy to discuss protest and activism.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
